GetPWASearchData

GetPWASearchData?PWA=Northern%20Adelaide%20Plains

See the Metadata - GetAdvancedListsData section for how to retrieve the valid PWA names.

Returns a list of wells as a JSON array of ojects:

GetPWAFromName

There is also the GetPWAFromName?NAME=Northern%20Adelaide%20Plains request, which returns data for the geographical shape of the PWA.

The Boundary string which is returned is the geographical boundary in Google’s Encoded Polyline Algorithm Format. You can decode this into geographic coordinates using the polyline package.
